<Page
  title="Sweet Bakes Chicago - Picture Gallery of our Extravagant Designs and Custom Cakes."
  description="Explore the different cakes we have made over the years and let it inspire your next cake design!"
>

<main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
  <header class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16 space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--color-brand-brown)]">
        Our Creations
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-brand-dark-brown)] leading-relaxed">
        From intricately decorated sugar cookies to our signature fluffy donuts, every treat at 
        <strong>Sweet Bakes Chicago</strong> is a work of art. We specialize in creating 
        custom desserts for weddings, birthdays, and special events across the Chicago area.
      </p>

    </header>
   

    <section class="photo-grid-section">
